<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="it">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Admin Login - Subscription Service</title>
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 1rem;
    }

    .login-container {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      padding: 3rem;
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 400px;
    }

    .login-header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .login-header h1 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      color: #232946;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .login-header p {
      color: #666;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .form-group {
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    label {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: #333;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    input[type="password"] {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 0.75rem;
      border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      transition: border-color 0.3s;
    }

    input[type="password"]:focus,
    input[type="text"]:focus {
      outline: none;
      border-color: #667eea;
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.1);
    }

    input[type="text"] {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 0.75rem;
      border: 2px solid #e0e0e0;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      transition: border-color 0.3s;
    }

    .submit-btn {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 0.85rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    }

    .submit-btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.3);
    }

    .submit-btn:active {
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    .error-message {
      color: #d32f2f;
      background: #ffebee;
      border: 1px solid #ef5350;
      padding: 0.75rem;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      text-align: center;
      display: none;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }

    .info-message {
      background: #e8f5e9;
      border-left: 4px solid #4caf50;
      padding: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #2e7d32;
    }

    .footer-text {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      color: #666;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }

    .token-section {
      background: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 1rem;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin-top: 2rem;
      display: none;
    }

    .token-section.show {
      display: block;
    }

    .token-label {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #666;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .token-display {
      background: white;
      padding: 0.75rem;
      border-radius: 4px;
      border: 1px solid #ddd;
      word-break: break-all;
      font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: #333;
      max-height: 150px;
      overflow-y: auto;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .copy-btn {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 0.5rem;
      background: #4caf50;
      color: white;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }

    .copy-btn:hover {
      background: #45a049;
    }

    .usage-instructions {
      background: #fff3cd;
      border: 1px solid #ffc107;
      padding: 1rem;
      border-radius: 6px;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #856404;
    }

    .usage-instructions h3 {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      color: #704214;
    }

    .usage-instructions ul {
      margin-left: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .usage-instructions li {
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="login-container">
    <div class="login-header">
      <h1>üîê Admin Panel</h1>
      <p>Subscription Service</p>
    </div>

    <div class="error-message" id="errorMessage"></div>

    <form id="loginForm" method="POST" action="/admin/login">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="username">Username</label>
        <input
          type="text"
          id="username"
          name="username"
          placeholder="Inserisci l'username di admin"
          required
          autocomplete="username"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="password">Password</label>
        <input
          type="password"
          id="password"
          name="password"
          placeholder="Inserisci la password di admin"
          required
          autocomplete="current-password"
        />
      </div>

      <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Accedi</button>
    </form>

    <div class="token-section" id="tokenSection">
      <div class="token-label">Token JWT (valido per 24 ore):</div>
      <div class="token-display" id="tokenDisplay"></div>
      <button type="button" class="copy-btn" onclick="copyToken()">Copia Token</button>

      <div class="usage-instructions">
        <h3>Come usare il token:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Nel browser:</strong> Aggiungi il token nell'header Authorization</li>
          <li><strong>In Postman:</strong> Vai nella tab Headers e aggiungi:
            <ul>
              <li>Key: <code>Authorization</code></li>
              <li>Value: <code>Bearer [token]</code></li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li><strong>Con cURL:</strong> <code>curl -H "Authorization: Bearer [token]" http://localhost:8004/admin</code></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
        <button type="button" class="submit-btn" onclick="accessAdmin()">Accedi all'Admin Panel</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-text">
      Questa pagina √® protetta. Utilizza solo credenziali autorizzate.
    </div>
  </div>

  </div>
</body>
</html>
